{"tid":902480,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"去西餐廳食，叫嘢飲係咪約定俗成?","createTime":"2018-11-14T23:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T13:28:04.000Z","uid":56561,"like":4,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0c6ea268ecea9c0af307add294069cf1c595e2","tid":902480,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T23:59:24.000Z","msg":"講緊得英文餐牌嗰種西餐廳，唔止香港，亦包括外國<br />\n<br />\n叫完 a la carte 嘢食後，有時就算講完 &quot;that's it&quot; 收尾， d 侍應都會問想叫咩嘢飲 (係問飲乜嘢 instead of 問要唔要叫嘢飲) ，亦見過隔離檯被鬼佬侍應親切有禮曲線地催佢地叫嘢飲<br />\n<br />\n唔叫嘢飲齋要 table water 係咪等同宣告cheap ，抑或只係餐廳嘅心理戰，畢竟 drinks 係最大 profit margin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09745838c09aff78e5f9b55ce5e04ed57935ce7","tid":902480,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"可以叫tap water既，但最好都跟返杯嘢飲<br />\n可以話係約定俗成既餐廳禮儀"},{"pid":"c6a29283b72fd2d5019b0a07c07a56a00a174867","tid":902480,"uid":43924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:03:22.000Z","msg":"試過叫兩杯tap water"},{"pid":"e90a0fc4e3321025d4a4c442676512d214aab66d","tid":902480,"uid":181272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:14:37.000Z","msg":"是一定要問咖啡或茶，唔問d鬼會反面。"},{"pid":"73c9e1da2bdcb1b4f261fdc4d1674beaa3cd9774","tid":902480,"uid":55810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:19:26.000Z","msg":"我永遠都話唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50db7119e88c9869f8482111b37676c5b29ab989","tid":902480,"uid":140802,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:25:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚貴 老閪都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bcda4ace2be1895acd8582cf8ca64cbd3dee7d","tid":902480,"uid":25069,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"坐低就叫杯飲品先啦<br />\n慢慢再叫嘢食"},{"pid":"6d31692f73591e49b8f4c3e953ae6c10473df707","tid":902480,"uid":27885,"